data.description: On this 1 Acre of Land sits a Nice large open floor plan Manuf. Dbl Wide Home w/a Bonus room-can be a 4th bedroom. Isolated Master Suite w/Jet Tub, Sep. Shower & Walkin Closet in bathroom. Spacious Kitchen w/a 1 WALL OVEN! large dining bar, corner desk/storage area & a small wet bar type cabinets & room for dining table or breakfast nook. Fairly New 1wall  oven  & refrigerator. Lots of light in kitchen. Large open Family Room w/Wood burning Fireplace. This home is on permanent foundation. Great for FHA or any special financing.  Seller is related to Listing Agent.
